        "label": "TITLE"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_010_110_000029",
    "sentence": "乙辛不得逞，謀以事誣皇后。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "乙辛",
        "label": "PER"
      },
      {
        "text": "皇后",
        "label": "TITLE"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_010_110_000030",
    "sentence": "后既死，乙辛不自安，又欲害太子。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "乙辛",
        "label": "PER"
      },
      {
        "text": "太子",
        "label": "TITLE"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_010_110_000031",
    "sentence": "乘間入奏曰：「帝與后如天地並位，中宮豈可曠？」",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_010_110_000032",
    "sentence": "盛稱其黨駙馬都尉蕭霞抹之妹美而賢。",
